content:
Posted: February 24
Early Access Review
								I purchased this game when it was Alpha 9.3; I have played SP for a long time before joining MP servers which got enjoyable. I also run a lightly modded MP PvE server with TS.. Its development is good for the most part. And we anticipate a better experience from TFP in the future.. Highly recommended, but keep in mind: It is in Alpha, so expect bugs;
